    "updated_at": "2025-02-27T13:56:53Z",
    "body": "in detail, seems there is the build time embedded in the binary:\n\n```\n$ strings target/release/starship  | grep build_time\nbuild_time:2025-02-27 14:27:08 +01:00\nbuild_time:2025-02-27 14:27:08 +01:00\n```\n\nwhile the `commit_hash` should be enough to identity the build.",
