    "created_at": "2025-03-03T10:20:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-03-03T10:20:38Z",
    "body": "Seems that `SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH` is supported indeed, so the non-determinism must be somewhere else. I'd close this issue for now, thanks All for the debugging help!\n\n```\n$ export SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH=123456\n\n$ cargo clean -q ; cargo build -q --release ; sha1sum target/release/starship\n2417d04f965ca2c76f5b91799366f2831ecbe3c0  target/release/starship\n\n$ cargo clean -q ; cargo build -q --release ; sha1sum target/release/starship \n2417d04f965ca2c76f5b91799366f2831ecbe3c0  target/release/starship\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
